ed="T" n="0838c04"/><persName key="A012516">釋圓震</persName>姓<name>陳</name>，<placeName key="PL000000002513">中山</placeName>人也。少<anchor xml:id="beg0838006"/>警悟<anchor xml:id="end0838006"/>而尚學，入<lb
ed="T" n="0838c05"/>庠序，研究五經。倏遇雲遊沙門寓宵，其父<lb
ed="T" n="0838c06"/>為州衙吏，酷有道心，留是僧供施。<persName key="A012516">震</persName>禮奉<lb
ed="T" n="0838c07"/>其僧，聽其談道，頗覺入神。捨<name>儒</name>典，披<name>釋</name><lb
ed="T" n="0838c08"/>經，頓辭所愛，往<placeName key="PL000000059338">白磁山</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0838sgsz21"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0838sgsz21"/><persName key="A012517">智幽</persName><ptr target="#n2642"/>為師受<lb
ed="T" n="0838c09"/>教<ptr target="#n2617"/>。後遇<persName key="A005612">荷澤<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>得法，隱<placeName key="PL000000025462"><placeName>南陽</placeName><placeName>烏牙山</placeName></placeName>。先<lb
ed="T" n="0838c10"/>是<ref type="place" target="#PL000000025462">山</ref>中多巨蛇，澤穴有毒龍，鄉人患之。<lb
ed="T" n="0838c11"/>及<persName key="A012516">震</persName>居此，二物潛蹤。曾有一人形服且異，<lb
ed="T" n="0838c12"/>致拜乃曰：「我在此已二百歲，今感無心之<lb
ed="T" n="0838c13"/>化，絕慮之修，吾曹冥感超昇，可非<ref type="person" target="#A012516">師</ref>之力<lb
ed="T" n="0838c14"/>歟！」<date from-iso="+0790-01-24" key="j20096252010008" to-iso="+0791-02-11"><name>貞元</name>六年</date>終，享齡八十六，弟子奉全身<lb
ed="T" n="0838c15"/>入塔焉。</p>
